&lt;li&gt;Design and ship high-quality features and product improvements in Figma’s core product surfaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to our design org’s culture by participating in design critiques, mentoring peers, and sharing best practices across teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
