&lt;h4&gt;We&#39;d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12+ years of experience leading global payroll operations in a public company environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of U.S. and international payroll laws, taxation, and compliance requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to design, implement, and maintain SOX-compliant controls and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership skills, with experience managing distributed teams and fostering growth through change&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work cross-functionally and influence decision-making at all levels of the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;While not required, it’s an added plus if you also have:&lt;/h4&gt;
