&lt;h2&gt;About the Role:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Partnerships Team at Vercel’s mission is to create mutual success for Vercel, our partners and customers. As the &lt;strong&gt;Director of Partnerships, North America&lt;/strong&gt;, you will own the success of Vercel’s partner ecosystem across global and regional channels managed from the North America region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate brings experience building strong partnerships in the composable ecosystem and thrives in a fast-paced, high-growth environment. This leadership role is mission-critical to expanding our partner ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;text-copy-16 text-gray-900 [&amp;amp;_b]:text-gray-1000 my-6 [&amp;amp;_b]:font-semibold [&amp;amp;_i]:not-italic&quot;&gt;If you’re based within a pre-determined commuting distance of one of our offices (SF, NY, London, or Berlin), the role includes in-office anchor days on Monday, Tuesday, and Friday. If you&#39;re located beyond that distance, the role is fully remote. For location-specific details, please connect with our recruiting team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and execute strategies that expand Vercel’s partner business through Technology Alliances and Solution Partner relationships, driving mutual growth and customer success.&lt;/li&gt;
