&lt;p&gt;As our Head of Product Marketing, you&#39;ll play a crucial role in driving our upmarket strategy, targeting large-scale, global enterprises. We&#39;re looking for a dynamic leader with &quot;LFG&quot; energy—someone who can inspire, innovate, and deliver results while mentoring and elevating our team.&lt;/p&gt;
