&lt;li&gt;Improve the developer experience for both small projects and large monorepos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay abreast of industry trends and advancements in CI/CD technologies, bringing innovative ideas to the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with the open-source community, participate in discussions, and contribute to related projects, aligning with Vercel&#39;s commitment to giving back to the developer community.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write clean, efficient, tested, and well-documented code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
