&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Vercel gives developers the tools and cloud infrastructure to build, scale, and secure a faster, more personalized web. As the team behind v0, Next.js, and AI SDK, Vercel helps customers like Ramp, Supreme, PayPal, Chick-fil-A, and Under Armour build for the AI-native web.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
